app_description: Filters and effects made for aesthetic storytellers around the world. Inspired by timeless style and the most popular trendsetters. LABS ONE CLICK. DONE. We have carefully created a wide range of presets that you will love! Minimal moody vintage BW influenced by popular trendsetters around the world. EXCLUSIVE FILTERS WITH BEAUTIFUL AESTHETICS We have worked hard to create photo filters you won t find anywhere else. TOOLS ADJUSTMENTS WITH EASE With our adjustment tools you can easily correct your photos to your liking. Fine tune the brightness contrast temperature highlights shadows sharpening skin tones cropping alignment saturation vibrance tint HSL EFFECTS FOR A REALISTIC LOOK Go beyond the ordinary look of your photos and get that trendy look with the market s best Film grain our unique Film blur multi option Motion Blur the super trendy Vintage Glow effect Un Focus for an imperfect look Low Pixels and Chromatic that will give your images a next level look. We have created advanced layers that integrate the text into the photo to give it that sophisticated premium look. At the same time the text gives your photos a minimalistic modern vibe. The text is editable so be creative and write what you want. LABBET FILTERS NO EDIT EDIT FILTER COLLECTION Subtle filters that give your photos an instant trendy look with fine adjustments of the colors in your photo. Super all round and works on pretty much any photo in your camera roll. BRIGHT FILTER COLLECTION Created to give your photos a brighter look. With the muted colors and a slightly blue ish tone this filter brings you a sophisticated artistic look. CHOCO FILTER COLLECTION This is all about earthy neutral tones. You just must try em! MOODY FILTER COLLECTION Low key moody looks are very trendy and we have nailed them for you! WARM FILTER COLLECTION Who likes warm and bright tones. Everyone! Right VINTAGE FILTER COLLECTION The vintage look will always be trendy and our collection won t disappoint you. We bring you a carefully designed collection of matte edits airy edits contrast rich edits and the highly popular disposable film look. FILM FILTER COLLECTION We can t get enough of film looks! Inspired by classic film stock we have created a brand new collection of filters suitable for all your photos. Combine with our super authentic Film Grain effect and your digital photos will get an analog classic look. BLACK WHITE FILTER COLLECTION We love the classic look that B W filters offer. We offer a collection of contrast rich matte warm and all round B W filters. Combined with our Grain tool you can create some really amazing photo edits.
